                                 : constructorTypeIR `< `# tid_impl* > `( `# id_default* )
  ---- ;; check instantiation convention
  -- Inst_ok:
      p TC_0 NAMED |- constructorTypeIR `< eps `# tid_impl* > `( argumentIR* `# id_default* )
                    : typeIR_object `< typeArgumentIR_inferred* > `( argumentIR_cast* )
